data.title: Galaxy Gymnastics
data.text:
Galaxy Gymnastics in Orangeburg, NY, was established in 1993 and is owned

by USA Gymnastics Region 6 - 2008 & 2010 coach of the year, Jamie Winkler. Located in the heart of Rockland County, offering classes for babies as young as 18 months old up through high school seniors in our state of the art facility. In addition we offer competitive team gymnastics.

We teach gymnastics and fitness in a fun, safe environment to foster a greater mind/body connection while teaching life lessons. We recognize that all children are individuals and learn at different speeds. Therefore, activities are personalized to give each boy and girl a chance to achieve to his or her full potential.

Developmental Program and

XCEL Gymnastics.

We have produced a number of State, Regional, and National Champions and many of our gymnasts go on to compete in college with gymnastics scholarships.
